```\r\nscheduler:\r\n  eventScheduler:\r\n    scheme: aws\r\n    region: \"us-east-1\"\r\n    scheduleRole: \"arn:aws:iam::{{ AWS_ACCOUNT_ID }}:role/flyte_cron_scheduler_role\"\r\n    targetName: \"arn:aws:sqs:us-east-1:{{ AWS_ACCOUNT_ID }}:flyte-cron-scheduler-queue\"\r\n  workflowExecutor:\r\n    scheme: aws\r\n    region: \"us-east-1\"\r\n    scheduleQueueName: \"flyte-cron-scheduler-queue\"\r\n    accountId: \"{{ AWS_ACCOUNT_ID }}\"  \r\n```\r\n2. Run FlyteAdmin and wait for this message (I don't know what was the reason and how to reproduce it) :) \r\n```{\"json\":{\"src\":\"base.go:138\"},\"level\":\"info\",\"msg\":\"Successfully started running the scheduled workflow executor\",\"ts\":\"2020-03-07T05:39:04Z\"}```\r\n\r\n**Environment**\r\n**Flyte component**\r\n- [+] Cloud hosted\r\n     * [+] AWS\r\n\r\n**Others**\r\nRestarting of the FlyteAdmin pod initialized new scheduledWorkflowExecutor and the SQS events were executed.\r\n\r\nThank you!","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/flyteorg/flyte/issues/198/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/flyteorg/flyte/issues/198/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go/issues/34230","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go/issues/34230/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go/issues/34230/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go/issues/34230/events","html_url":"https://github.com/golang/go/issues/34230","id":492181086,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU0OTIxODEwODY=","number":34230,"title":"x/tools/gopls: 'span' should support the import module path with upper-case","user":{"login":"movie-travel-code","id":5517506,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU1MTc1MDY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubu