tion mark is intended, see https://github.com/golang/go/issues/26456.\r\n```shell\r\n[Trace - 6:58:12 PM] Received response 'textDocument/definition - (5)' in 75ms.\r\nParams: [{\"uri\":\"file:///Users/henrywong/workspace/gopath/pkg/mod/github.com/%21shopify/sarama@v1.23.1/config.go\",\"range\":{\"start\":{\"line\":20,\"character\":5},\"end\":{\"line\":20,\"character\":11}}}]\r\n```\r\nvscode-go can handle this because of https://github.com/microsoft/vscode/blob/master/src/vs/base/common/uri.ts#L478. However I think it would be better convert the **%21** back to **!** when gopls reply the result to the clients.\r\n","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go/issues/34230/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go/issues/34230/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go/issues/33513","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go/issues/33513/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go/issues/33513/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/golang/go/issues/33513/events","html_url":"https://github.com/golang/go/issues/33513","id":477774975,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU0Nzc3NzQ5NzU=","number":33513,"title":"proxy.golang.org: problem with some modules related to golang.org/x/","user":{"login":"ldez","id":5674651,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU2NzQ2NTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5674651?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez","html_url":"https://github.com/ldez","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/us